==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Afoul
<hw>A*foul"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv. & a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>a-</ets> + <ets>foul</ets>.]</ety> <def>In collision;
entangled.</def> <rj><au>Totten.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>To run afoul of</b></col>, <cd>to run against or come
into collision with, especially so as to become entangled or to cause
injury.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Afraid</ent>⟦br⟧
